title: Marcel Proust - Remembrance of Things Past (Audiobook)
description:
Audiobook collection Vol. 1-7 of Marcel Proust's "Remembrance of Things Past"

Swann's Way [Naxos]
Within a Budding Grove
The Guermantes Way - Remembrance of Things Past, Volume 3
Sodom & Gomorrah (RoTP 4)
Captive, The (RoTP 5)
Fugitive, The (RoTP 6)
Time Regained (RoTP 7)


"Marcel Proust is best known for his 3000 page masterpiece À la recherche du temps perdu (Remembrance of Things Past or In Search of Lost Time), a pseudo-autobiographical novel told mostly in a stream-of-consciousness style."

Sources are neglected per-volume torrents.  File structure not modified
